HOW TO UPDATE ANTILOPE’S FIRMWARE:
While antilope is not powered, connect a micro usb cable between
your laptop and antilope’s port on the right side.
Power-up your antilope while holding the grey button on the side
of the usb port, hold for 1-2 seconds, then release it.
Antilope will appear as a usb device, drag and drop the .uf2
firmware file.
The usb device will eject on its own, you can now uplug the usb
micro cable.

Hail the donut,
MRC
